If you are looking to open a new account in QuickBooks, the first step is to call the QuickBooks help line. The QuickBooks help line is available 24/7 and can assist you with anything from creating a new account to resolving a problem. To make a call, simply dial (833) 983-2639 and provide your unique QuickBooks ID number. Alternatively, you can visit the QuickBooks website and enter your ID number into the “Create or Modify an Account” form on the home page. If you have questions about using your current account, be sure to check out our user guide. After calling or visiting the QuickBooks help line, be sure to read through our frequently asked questions for more information on how to use QuickBooks.
